In editor the function text font should transform to uppercase for all chars for specific language keywords.
string or String or STRING all work for the type but the editor should transform them to a specific color for the type and uppercase it.

Returns Error, Void, or String
FUNCTION example(arg: STRING = 'default') Error, VOID, STRING  {
	AWAIT fnThatCanBeAsyncByDefault();
	DEFER thisRunsAfterTheFunction();
	RETURN arg;
}
 Await, Defer, and Return should also all be automatically styled in the editor to decorate with uppercase. The case is insensitive.

This is a function shorthand by calling the function then providing the first argument it's the same as (''), (Any object)
Multiple arguments should instead use the traditional method of (argument, list, goes, here)
The semicolon is mandatory for all syntax to ensure a defined terminator and readable code.

This style is optional and some linters may disable this in favor of more consistent readable code.

